name: Custom Conversion: Military Tripod Floor Lamp
description:
At Industrial Electric Light Company we offer a full lighting conversion service, bringing light and life to your old antiques and interesting finds. 

We will work with you to create a light to your exact specification, we have hundreds of options from industrial cleaning to bring back that beautiful shine, to bulb styles and different colour fabric cables. We have worked in many commercial environments from bars and restaurants to hotels and shops, to create that perfect look for the client. If you have an item that you would like converted we are more than happy to take a look at it for you and give you a price.

Just email the details of your item attaching as many pictures as you can plus the overall dimensions to hello@industrialelectric.co.uk and our design team will come straight back to you.
